++++# Layout:
++++#   nvs        24 KB   non-volatile storage (WiFi creds, config)
++++#   phy_init    4 KB   RF calibration
++++#   otadata     8 KB   OTA slot selection
++++#   ota_0      3 MB   factory application (A/B slot A)
++++#   ota_1      3 MB   OTA application (A/B slot B)
++++#   littlefs  ~1 MB   show bundle (.shw1) + Preact web console
++++#   coredump  512 KB  panic core dumps (robustness)
